  <entry>
    <title>Android基础</title>
    <url>/2021/04/06/Android%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>终于开始安卓学习了<br>接受了一晚上地焦虑信息输入，下次Kotlin和Flutter要一起加油了<br>做了很多工具式的事情，弄了些插件学了些使用方法现在感觉敲代码更加快乐了<br>想要快点开发一个自己的APP嘻嘻虽然不知道要搞什么<br>JAVA也要准备学习WEB内容了<br>不过这之前先在这个周末把数据库编程学了<br>可恶中午午觉起来去图书馆自习突然发现图书馆不能刷手机进去了要一卡通<br>还走了好多路呢</p>
<span id="more"></span>
<h1 id="Android开发学习"><a href="#Android开发学习" class="headerlink" title="Android开发学习"></a>Android开发学习</h1><h2 id="Kotlin基础"><a href="#Kotlin基础" class="headerlink" title="Kotlin基础"></a>Kotlin基础</h2><p>确实确实</p>
<p>终于开始学习安卓开发了，先学习的Kotlin基础知识</p>
<p>变量初始化还蛮奇怪的</p>
<figure class="highlight kotlin"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">val</span> Student1 = Student(<span class="number">99</span>,<span class="number">1910301008</span>,<span class="string">&quot;zuoqiumama&quot;</span>,<span class="number">20</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">val</span> Teacher1 = Teacher(<span class="string">&quot;math&quot;</span>,<span class="number">10110</span>,<span class="string">&quot;qiuqiuma&quot;</span>,<span class="number">24</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>val表示不可变，而var代表可变，在变量名后面加个冒号加个变量类型再加个等号＝啥啥的差不多就是变量初始化了，Kotlin有非常强大的类型推导，所以不太需要表明类型。</p>
<figure class="highlight kotlin"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">interface</span> <span class="title">move</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">fun</span> <span class="title">eat</span><span class="params">(obj: <span class="type">String</span>)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        println(<span class="keyword">this</span>.toString()+<span class="string">&quot;is eating <span class="variable">$obj</span>&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">fun</span> <span class="title">run</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        println(<span class="keyword">this</span>.toString()+<span class="string">&quot;is running&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>这个是接口说明，在Kotlin中的接口可以有默认实现，有了默认实现的函数不需要在继承该接口的类中进行重载</p>
<figure class="highlight kotlin"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">open</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">People</span></span>(<span class="keyword">var</span> name:String,age:<span class="built_in">Int</span> ):move</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>在Kotlin中类不加修饰的都是不可被继承的，控制类能不能继承是个好习惯。</p>
<p>在JAVA中，不可继承的类最好加入final修饰</p>
<p>open代表类可以被继承</p>
<p>data数据类，自动给你hashcode，toString,eaquels函数配置好，</p>
<p>object表示单例类，就是只有一个实例的类</p>
<p>另外Kotlin的构造函数可以直接在类名后面加括号，类的内容也可以在括号里面添加</p>
<figure class="highlight kotlin"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Student</span></span>(<span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">val</span> grade:<span class="built_in">Int</span>, <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">val</span> id:<span class="built_in">Int</span>, name:String, age : <span class="built_in">Int</span>):People(name, age) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="function"><span class="keyword">fun</span> <span class="title">showGrade</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        println(<span class="string">&quot;this student<span class="variable">$id</span> grade is<span class="variable">$grade</span>&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="comment">// override  fun toString():String = &quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>看这个就知道构造函数把类要的都包含了，后面两个参数不加val或者var就是区别是不是这个类的参数</p>
<p>Kotlin还有个次构造函数，但这个构造函数一定要调用主构造函数，其实这个初始化方式可以用给主构造函数默认值解决</p>
<p>从这个代码块里面看，还有个字符串嵌入这一个语法糖，美元符号后面就是变量值输出</p>
<h2 id="Android基础"><a href="#Android基础" class="headerlink" title="Android基础"></a>Android基础</h2><p>开始安卓基础学了真的真的真的</p>
<p>先接触的就是Activity这个东西，mainActivity就是APP点开调用的东西</p>
<figure class="highlight kotlin"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">override</span> <span class="function"><span class="keyword">fun</span> <span class="title">onCreate</span><span class="params">(savedInstanceState: <span class="type">Bundle</span>?)</span></span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">super</span>.onCreate(savedInstanceState)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//setContentView(R.layout.firstlayout)</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//viewBinding绑定视图</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">val</span> binding = FirstlayoutBinding.inflate(layoutInflater)</span><br><span class="line">    setContentView(binding.root)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">//直接用binding调用组件设置相关内容</span></span><br><span class="line">    binding.button1.setOnClickListener &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        Toast.makeText(<span class="keyword">this</span>,<span class="string">&quot;Binding Test Click&quot;</span>, Toast.LENGTH_SHORT).show()</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">/*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    //获取按钮</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    val button1:Button = findViewById(R.id.start_button)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    //监听按钮</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">    button1.setOnClickListener&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">        //按钮点击的事件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">        Toast.makeText(this,&quot;click button once&quot;,Toast.LENGTH_SHORT).show()</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">     */</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>这里就不得不吐槽下Google技术更新换代的快了QAQ</p>
<p>本来原来方法是用findViewById这个方法找到布局里的元素比如按钮等</p>
<p>最新版的书还写着用一个插件直接根据元素的id调用布局文件里面的元素，结果官方取消了这个默认方法，</p>
<p>改成了用ViewBinding的方法</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;Button</span><br><span class="line">    android:id&#x3D;&quot;@+id&#x2F;button1&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    android:layout_width&#x3D;&quot;match_parent&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    android:layout_height&#x3D;&quot;wrap_content&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    android:text&#x3D;&quot;START&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    &#x2F;&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>比如说这个是layout的按钮信息</p>
<p>在App文件里面的build.gradle里加入</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">buildFeatures &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    viewBinding true</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>就可以让元素像上面</p>
<p>binding.button1.setOnClickListener {<br>        Toast.makeText(this,”Binding Test Click”, Toast.LENGTH_SHORT).show()<br>    }</p>
<p>一样调用设置监听</p>
<p>然后还设置了菜单</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;item android:id&#x3D;&quot;@+id&#x2F;add_item&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    android:title&#x3D;&quot;@string&#x2F;add&quot;&#x2F;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;item android:id&#x3D;&quot;@+id&#x2F;remove_item&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    android:title&#x3D;&quot;@string&#x2F;remove&quot;&#x2F;&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight kotlin"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">override</span> <span class="function"><span class="keyword">fun</span> <span class="title">onCreateOptionsMenu</span><span class="params">(menu: <span class="type">Menu</span>?)</span></span>: <span class="built_in">Boolean</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    menuInflater.inflate(R.menu.main,menu)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">override</span> <span class="function"><span class="keyword">fun</span> <span class="title">onOptionsItemSelected</span><span class="params">(item: <span class="type">MenuItem</span>)</span></span>: <span class="built_in">Boolean</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">/**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">     * 对when的复习吧</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">     * 控制菜单的点击事件</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">     */</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">when</span>(item.itemId)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        R.id.add_item-&gt;Toast.makeText(<span class="keyword">this</span>,<span class="string">&quot;click add &quot;</span>,Toast.LENGTH_SHORT).show()</span><br><span class="line">        R.id.remove_item-&gt;Toast.makeText(<span class="keyword">this</span>,<span class="string">&quot;click remove&quot;</span>,Toast.LENGTH_SHORT).show()</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>这个就是创建一个菜单，然后监听这个菜单事件</p>
<p>这些都是很简单易懂的很难扩展说明</p>
<p>学到后面我都不知道inflate是什么意思、、</p>
<p>感觉翻译软件不太好用</p>
<p>说到翻译软件就不得不夸夸插件</p>
<p>IDEA的插件（彩虹括号，主题，彩虹小马）和Edge插件（VPN，油猴脚本—直接免费看VIP）都太好用了</p>
<p>还有2021、4、6我把IDEA的完整版给破解了嘻嘻嘻，现在昂贵的IDEA可以用到2099年</p>
<p>一会再把IDEA的插件搞下我就可以心满意足地去睡觉了</p>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>Android</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>-Kotlin</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>JAVA 网络编程</title>
    <url>/2021/03/22/JAVA%20%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>再不写Blog我就都快忘记我学什么了。<br>安卓还没开始学QAQ<br>我明天白天要把多线程的书看完。<br>晚上继续学网课，在周末之前学完网课<br>体育要拍视频作业QAQAQAQAQAQAQAQAQAQAQ<br>网络编程写玩了是不是可以用SWING写个聊天软件？</p>
<span id="more"></span>
<h1 id="JAVA-网络编程"><a href="#JAVA-网络编程" class="headerlink" title="JAVA 网络编程"></a>JAVA 网络编程</h1><h3 id="UDP"><a href="#UDP" class="headerlink" title="UDP"></a>UDP</h3><p>很简单快捷的，不需要很好的网络条件进行//网课好像是这么描述的</p>
<p>冷知识：QQ一开始是UDP来的</p>
<p>这个只需要打开网络通道</p>
<p>数据打包发送</p>
<p>接受数据就可以了</p>
<p>具体如下</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">DatagramSocket datagramSocket = <span class="keyword">new</span> DatagramSocket(<span class="number">3000</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">byte</span>[] buf = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="keyword">byte</span>[<span class="number">1024</span>];</span><br><span class="line">DatagramPacket datagramPacket = <span class="keyword">new</span> DatagramPacket(buf,<span class="number">1024</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>Socket打开了网络通道，端口是3000；</p>
<p>然后Packet存储的数据流在byte数组里</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">datagramSocket.receive(datagramPacket);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>将连接的端发来的数据放入Packet里。</p>
<p>然后对这个包进行操作就可以了</p>
<p>发送数据就</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">datagramSocket.send(datagramPacket1);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>这个就能发送了。</p>
<p>另外一个顺序反过来就可以进行双向交替进行。</p>
<p>启动这个建议先启动接收端，不然发送端先发送后，接收端没启动可能数据会丢失</p>
<h3 id="TCP"><a href="#TCP" class="headerlink" title="TCP"></a>TCP</h3><p>这个网络相率更高，但是成本高，安全</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BufferedReader bufferedReader = <span class="keyword">new</span> BufferedReader(<span class="keyword">new</span> InputStreamReader(socket.getInputStream()));</span><br><span class="line">DataOutputStream dos =  <span class="keyword">new</span> DataOutputStream(socket.getOutputStream());</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>这个创建输入流和输出流的读取器</p>
<p>服务器启动后，客户和服务器的输入输出流是相互的。</p>
<p>然后对输入输出流进行操作就可以了。</p>
<p>采用多线程就可以一个服务器对多个人了（也许是多线程实现的）</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ServerSocket serverSocket = <span class="keyword">new</span> ServerSocket(<span class="number">8001</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">//ThreadPoolExecutor executor = (ThreadPoolExecutor) Executors.newFixedThreadPool(6);</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span>(<span class="keyword">true</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    Socket socket = serverSocket.accept();</span><br><span class="line">    System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;come to a client&quot;</span>+socket.getInetAddress().getHostAddress());</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">new</span> Thread(<span class="keyword">new</span> TcpClient(socket)).start();</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>本来是打算用excutor实现固定线程实现的。因为线程不固定，大量用户访问会对服务器造成伤害</p>
<p>而客户端只需要在来个输入流取向系统输入就可以了，这样用系统输入操作完就交给输出流发送给服务器，服务器再读取输入流。</p>
<p>下面是客户端</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">TCPClient</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">(String args[])</span> <span class="keyword">throws</span> IOException </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        Socket socket = <span class="keyword">new</span> Socket(InetAddress.getByName(<span class="string">&quot;127.0.0.1&quot;</span>),<span class="number">8001</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        BufferedReader bufferedReader = <span class="keyword">new</span> BufferedReader(<span class="keyword">new</span> InputStreamReader(socket.getInputStream()));</span><br><span class="line">        DataOutputStream dataOutputStream = <span class="keyword">new</span> DataOutputStream(socket.getOutputStream());</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        BufferedReader bufferedReaderByKey = <span class="keyword">new</span> BufferedReader(<span class="keyword">new</span> InputStreamReader(System.in));</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span>(<span class="keyword">true</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            String readLine = bufferedReaderByKey.readLine();</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span>(readLine.equalsIgnoreCase(<span class="string">&quot;quit&quot;</span>))&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;I said &quot;</span>+readLine);</span><br><span class="line">            dataOutputStream.writeBytes(readLine+System.getProperty(<span class="string">&quot;line.separator&quot;</span>));</span><br><span class="line">            System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;System said &quot;</span>+bufferedReader.readLine());</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        bufferedReader.close();</span><br><span class="line">        bufferedReaderByKey.close();</span><br><span class="line">        dataOutputStream.close();</span><br><span class="line">        socket.close();</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>好了好像就学了这些？可能只前学的没有记住。</p>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>JAVA</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>网络编程</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>JAVA GSON文件读写</title>
    <url>/2021/03/22/JAVA%20JSON%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E8%AF%BB%E5%86%99/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>趁着断电之前赶出来了QAQ<br>是的文件读写和多线程要放放了</p>
<span id="more"></span>
<h1 id="JAVA-JSON文件读写"><a href="#JAVA-JSON文件读写" class="headerlink" title="JAVA JSON文件读写"></a>JAVA JSON文件读写</h1><p>这个json是几天前学的东西了有点忘了</p>
<h4 id="JSON的特性"><a href="#JSON的特性" class="headerlink" title="JSON的特性"></a>JSON的特性</h4><p>JSON比XML更加轻便，表示也很方便</p>
<p>{}是一个对象内容</p>
<p>【】是数组</p>
<figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;school name&quot;</span>:<span class="string">&quot;newschool&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;teacher&quot;</span>:<span class="string">&quot;&#123;\&quot;teahcer2\&quot;:\&quot;&#123;\\\&quot;name\\\&quot;:\\\&quot;张老师\\\&quot;,\\\&quot;id\\\&quot;:2&#125;\&quot;,\&quot;student\&quot;:[\&quot;&#123;\\\&quot;name\\\&quot;:\\\&quot;sdfcxd\\\&quot;,\\\&quot;id\\\&quot;:4&#125;,&#123;\\\&quot;name\\\&quot;:\\\&quot;shyhij\\\&quot;,\\\&quot;id\\\&quot;:655&#125;\&quot;]&#125;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>这个就是我写的JSON的文件。</p>
<p>很显然有BUG但我决定为了多线程的学习把文件读写推后学了</p>
<p>处理JSON在JAVA里有GSON 这个包，<del>网课里介绍这个包比较好用所以别的我就没有学嘻嘻</del></p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Gson gson &#x3D; new Gson();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>这个创建一个gson对象这样可以将一个类的信息和JSON文件信息相互转换（也许是我还没有尝试把一个JSON文件信息转换成类</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">JsonObject newSchool = <span class="keyword">new</span> JsonObject();</span><br><span class="line">newSchool.addProperty(<span class="string">&quot;school name&quot;</span>,<span class="string">&quot;newschool&quot;</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>实例化一个jsonObject，这样就可在这个对象上创建JSON实例，比如我可以addProperty创建一个school  name信息，并给他赋值。这就很想HashMap键值配对</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">JsonArray stuArr = <span class="keyword">new</span> JsonArray();</span><br><span class="line">JsonArray stuArr2 = <span class="keyword">new</span> JsonArray();</span><br><span class="line">String stu1 = gson.toJson(student1)+<span class="string">&quot;,&quot;</span>+gson.toJson(student2);</span><br><span class="line">String stu2 = gson.toJson(student3)+<span class="string">&quot;,&quot;</span>+gson.toJson(student4);</span><br><span class="line">stuArr.add(stu1);</span><br><span class="line">stuArr2.add(stu2);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>我尝试着做两个学生JSON数组，</p>
<p>很明显是做出来了</p>
<p>但是效果不是很感觉QAQ</p>
<p>因为在我尝试把学生数组插入给教师</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">objTeacher1.add(<span class="string">&quot;student&quot;</span>,stuArr);</span><br><span class="line">objTeacher2.add(<span class="string">&quot;student&quot;</span>,stuArr2);</span><br><span class="line">newSchool.addProperty(<span class="string">&quot;teacher&quot;</span>, gson.toJson(objTeacher1));</span><br><span class="line">newSchool.addProperty(<span class="string">&quot;teacher&quot;</span>, gson.toJson(objTeacher2));</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>失败了，好像是两个学生数组插入到一个老师里面了</p>
<p>而且整个school里面我创建了2个老师，但是最后输出却只有1个老师</p>
<p>无所谓了以后再说</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">File file = <span class="keyword">new</span> File(<span class="string">&quot;GsonTest.json&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">FileWriter writer = <span class="keyword">new</span> FileWriter(file);</span><br><span class="line">writer.append(gson.toJson(newSchool));</span><br><span class="line">writer.close();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>笑死，根本不会文件读写</p>
<h1 id="JAVA-多线程"><a href="#JAVA-多线程" class="headerlink" title="JAVA 多线程"></a>JAVA 多线程</h1><p>然后就是多线程了</p>
<p>根据网课给的一个生物系统生产者不断生产资源，和捕食者不断在生态系统中掠夺资源，形成一个动态资源。</p>
<p>我自己写了一个存款人和取款人不断在一个银行里存款取款的方法。</p>
<p>先是一个银行</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">double</span>[] accounts;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> Lock bankLock = <span class="keyword">new</span> ReentrantLock();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>accounts模拟一个银行多个账户，存款人和取款人各2个每个都是线程。</p>
<p>//不是的上面是转账的，搞错了。用了普通的锁，也许在并发1里讲过了。</p>
<p>下面的才是存款取款人</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">volatile</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">int</span> money;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="keyword">int</span> upperLimit;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>volatile表示这个域每次改变 ，获得这个域的线程都能实时地变，不会出错。</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">synchronized</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">drawMoney</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> theMoney)</span> <span class="keyword">throws</span> InterruptedException </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>((money - theMoney)&lt; <span class="number">0</span> )&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        System.out.println(<span class="string">&quot;Money is not enough&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        wait();</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    money -= theMoney;</span><br><span class="line">    System.out.print(Thread.currentThread().getName());</span><br><span class="line">    Bank.totalMoney();</span><br><span class="line">    notifyAll();</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>这个就是取款人的取款动作，银行提供取钱功能给取款人使用。当钱不够想要取的钱的时候这个事件就会等待满足条件后再进行，wait()就是实现这个功能的。在功能最后，也就是取款完，唤醒其它可能存在的等待线程。例如因为<del>银行钱存满了</del> 而等待的存款人事件。告诉他们事情做完了，让调控器选择合适的线程进行启动。</p>
<p>存款人和这个行为很像。</p>
<p>然后在主函数启动4个线程就可以了嘻嘻。</p>
<h2 id="excutor"><a href="#excutor" class="headerlink" title="excutor"></a>excutor</h2><p>一个设计好的线程池框架</p>
<p>本来我自己想用普通的Thread的线程，实现6个线程计算10到1000的累加</p>
<p>然后怎么算都是错的</p>
<p>我放弃了</p>
<p>然后看到了excutor框架</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ThreadPoolExecutor executor = (ThreadPoolExecutor) Executors.newFixedThreadPool(<span class="number">6</span>);</span><br><span class="line">List&lt;Future&lt;Double&gt;&gt; resultList = <span class="keyword">new</span> ArrayList&lt;&gt;();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>第一个是确定线程池里最多有几个线程</p>
<p>第二个是存放一个result的数组</p>
<p>excutor和Runnable的区别就在于excutor需要覆盖的call方法可以有返回值，而run不需要。他们作为方法一个由excutor.submit提交就可以运行线程。而run由线程start开始运行。</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="keyword">int</span> i =<span class="number">0</span> ; i &lt; <span class="number">10</span>; i++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    Sumer sumer = <span class="keyword">new</span> Sumer(<span class="number">10</span>*i+<span class="number">1</span>,(i+<span class="number">1</span>)*<span class="number">10</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    Future&lt;Double&gt; result = executor.submit(sumer);</span><br><span class="line">    resultList.add(result);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>这样就能把结果存进数组里，然后要得到最终结果只需要遍历数组就可以了。</p>
<h2 id="Fork-join"><a href="#Fork-join" class="headerlink" title="Fork-join"></a>Fork-join</h2><p>也许是这个框架，刚学，不熟，还没实现</p>
<p>而且后面的多线程课程，我书本里更详细。</p>
<p>就是条件控制定时和锁。书里先讲了这些。</p>
<p>以后再说。</p>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>JAVA</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>-XML -多线程</tag>
      </tags>
